SIMPLE: superannuation
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superannuation
<hw>Su`per*an`nu*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state
of being superannuated, or too old for office or business; the state of
being disqualified by old age; decrepitude.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The world itself is in a state of <qex>superannuation</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Slyness blinking through the watery eye of
<qex>superannuation</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superb</ent>⟦br⟧
